{"tid":56494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［肥婆］我愛上在Instagram上搜尋「單身」。","createTime":"2016-12-27T09:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T09:37:44.000Z","uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca4dd590a09d9108641b539ea7770255b2e07672","tid":56494,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"係Instagram上所謂招朋友呢啲5P嘢已經屢見不鮮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最近我真係好鐘意上去睇呢啲Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如咁，有啲肥婆得160仲要肥撚過閪，但個招友Post都係要話自己正常身型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/171805_0da4d24498c8a74d7629f4e302e60c9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F171805_0da4d24498c8a74d7629f4e302e60c9d.jpg&h=10835b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又或者有啲肥婆會標榜自己係「小肥」，知唔知乜撚嘢叫小肥呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小肥係可愛、有肉地，而唔撚係肥撚到漏油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然可能你會話我又未見過佢地啲相或者真人，點解會認為人地一定係肥婆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你諗諗有咩人會係現實世界識唔到男仔，要用Instagram出撚埋呢啲5P叫春Post，仲要古撚惑到唔出樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再者佢班死肥婆仲要要求多多，又要乖仔唔煙唔酒唔粗口唔咸濕，又要靚仔高大夾威猛。你諗下啦，如果你現實之中靚撚到啪啪聲你當然可以開呢啲Offer啦，但你正正就係無咁嘅資格先要上Instagram叫春吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/27/173256_232690ba0010514f2fccbe5c1a8bcf95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F27%2F173256_232690ba0010514f2fccbe5c1a8bcf95.jpg&h=54fedfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後就係一班初中雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 13-4歲就學人出5P Post，仲要明碼實價寫明擇偶要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果然港女現實勢利嘅眼光係由細所培養出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2505de133f746aa22d8991b1b3c97cfc9d98e7ab","tid":56494,"uid":32979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:37:44.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}